Package: HGNCREST
Title: Query the HGNC API with httr2
Version: 0.99.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Marcel", "Ramos", , "marcel.ramos@sph.cuny.edu", c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3242-0582"))
    )
Description: Query the HGNC API with httr2. The HGNC API provides access to data
  from the HGNC database, which contains information about human genes. The
  package provides functions to query the HGNC API and retrieve data about
  genes, gene families, and gene symbols. The package also provides functions to
  retrieve data about gene symbols from the HGNC database.
